verses.verse: A Psalm<WH4210> of David.<WH1732> Give<WH3051> to the LORD,<WH3068> O you mighty,<WH1121> <WH410> give<WH3051> to the LORD<WH3068> glory<WH3519> and strength.<WH5797>
